wiki.content: "Ooh La La" is a song by Britney Spears, recorded as a gift to her two sons and Smurf fans Sean Preston and Jayden James. It was included in The Smurfs 2 film and soundtrack. The bubblegum, summer-pop style track was produced by Dr. Luke and features background vocals from Katy Perry and Bonnie McKee.
